```
⚙️ *Executor — {TODAY} 4:30 PM IST*

*Actions fired:*
1. {type} on {target} — {result, e.g. "shipped commit abc1234"}
2. {type} on {target} — {result}

*Watches added:*
• {watch ID} → check {date}

*Skipped (filtered):*
• {action} — {reason, e.g. "ANTI-PATTERN AP4: page modified 5 days ago"}

*Backlog remaining:*
